{"tid":750573,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先physical班女柒到核爆","createTime":"2018-07-21T04:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T12:52:04.000Z","uid":11779,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5161078810ada9ceb5c56bad6d68e61e909fd6","tid":750573,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"話說physical班女成鳩日係啲common area 自己又跳票又拉筋阻鳩住晒，仲以為自己好吸引。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁頭先係physical又冇班女係度扭屎忽 啲袋又放係啲機度阻住晒我地正經做，咁有個勁大隻嘅師兄望住佢地，佢地就以為人地㗳佢糖 對住果位師兄笑左下 跟住跳得仲high仲自信，心諗一班40-50嘅大嬸係度扭屎忽好樣衰呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果位師兄終於頂唔順好禮貌咁左句：你地介唔介意行開？因為你地阻住我地用機呀。<br />\n<br />\n班女塊面即時臭過馬桶 死死氣咁行開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗佢地那裡來的自信覺得人地望佢係因為佢地性感。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d4cc611c27bf614a4141e2992a3d7a0f88a4d6","tid":750573,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e7ae5a59b7cdc0417f06927f9b915773b2e955","tid":750573,"uid":194666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56d4cc611c27bf614a4141e2992a3d7a0f88a4d6","tid":750573,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"大隻ching Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"